English: Gather GLP-2 canisters and go to the forward exit point.
Description: A text string that appears on screen when the player attempts to open a door which is locked due to an emergency lockdown. Don't alter the RichText tags.

French.Translation: Rassemblez des bombes de GLP-2 et rendez-vous au point de sortie.

Italian.Translation: Raccogliere bombole GLP-2 e raggiungere il punto d'estrazione anteriore.

German.Translation: Sammeln Sie GLP-2-Kanister und begeben Sie sich zum vorderen Austrittspunkt.

Spanish.Translation: Reúne recipientes de GLP-2 y ve al punto de evacuación.

Russian.Translation: Соберите канистры с ГПП-2 и идите к точке выхода.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Colete recipientes GLP-2 e avance para o próximo ponto de saída.

Polish.Translation: Zbierz kanistry GLP-2 i przejdź do punktu ewakuacyjnego.

Japanese.Translation: GLP-2缶を集めて先の脱出地点へ行け。

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 收集GLP-2罐並前往前進撤離點。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 收集GLP-2罐并去往前出口处。
